<p>All courses in the minor have prerequisites equivalent to <span class="sc_courseinline"><span class="code_bubble" data-code-bubble="MAT 021A">MAT 021A</span></span>-<span class="sc_courseinline"><span class="code_bubble" data-code-bubble="MAT 021B">MAT 021B</span></span>-<span class="sc_courseinline"><span class="code_bubble" data-code-bubble="MAT 021C">MAT 021C</span></span>-<span class="sc_courseinline"><span class="code_bubble" data-code-bubble="MAT 021D">MAT 021D</span></span> and <span class="sc_courseinline"><span class="code_bubble" data-code-bubble="MAT 022A">MAT 022A</span></span>-<span class="sc_courseinline"><span class="code_bubble" data-code-bubble="MAT 022B">MAT 022B</span></span> and <span class="sc_courseinline"><span class="code_bubble" data-code-bubble="PHY 009A">PHY 009A</span></span>-<span class="sc_courseinline"><span class="code_bubble" data-code-bubble="PHY 009B">PHY 009B</span></span>-<span class="sc_courseinline"><span class="code_bubble" data-code-bubble="PHY 009C">PHY 009C</span></span>-<span class="sc_courseinline"><span class="code_bubble" data-code-bubble="PHY 009D">PHY 009D</span></span>.</p>

