<quickviewtext name="Quick View">
<![CDATA[
<p>From subatomic particles to galaxies with billions of stars, physics studies what the universe is made of and how it works. As a Physics minor, you learn about our present understanding of the universe and also have the opportunity to join with our faculty in research that pushes forward the frontier of knowledge.</p>
